# Agent Policies – AnaCredit System

## 1. Referential Integrity Agent
- Validates relationships between datasets
- Uses rules: RI0030, RI0040, RI0050, RI0060
- Ensures data linkage between tables

## 2. Completeness Agent
- Checks missing mandatory fields
- Uses rules: CM001, CM002, CM003

## 3. Consistency Agent
- Validates logical correctness
- Uses rules: CN001, CN002

## 4. Plausibility Agent
- Detects anomalies and suspicious data
- Uses rules: PL001, PL002, PL003

## 5. RAG Autofix Agent
- Uses rules + historical fixes
- Suggests corrections

## 6. Policy Engine
- Reads rules from Excel/JSON
- Converts rules into executable checks
